00:27:03.965 --> 00:27:06.005
roaming poor fences, kids

566
00:27:06.005 --> 00:27:08.045
and dogs unsupervised together, fear

567
00:27:08.065 --> 00:27:09.605
and pain in the dog go unaddressed.

