00:27:09.905 --> 00:27:12.725
Bottom line, a behavior-based approach is more accurate,

569
00:27:12.945 --> 00:27:14.245
fairer, and more effective.

570
00:27:14.665 --> 00:27:17.405
It targets actual risk in front of us and not stereotypes.

