575
00:27:27.285 --> 00:27:29.265
The most practical way to do that is

576
00:27:29.265 --> 00:27:31.865
to adapt an objective bite severity scale.

577
00:27:32.685 --> 00:27:36.265
So one best known is the Dr N Dunbar dog bite Scale.

578
00:27:36.645 --> 00:27:39.865
As Melinda's already talked about, a classifies incidents

579
00:27:39.865 --> 00:27:42.065
by the wounds caused not by the dog's type,

580
00:27:42.235 --> 00:27:43.545
which reduces guesswork

581
00:27:43.545 --> 00:27:45.825
and helps decisions be consistent and defensible.

